		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I wish there was a 16-bit RISC CPU that competed in price with the 65816.  I think a RISC architecture with 8 16-bit registers and both a 16 bit data and address bus would've been pretty close to the 65816 in price.  If you think about, the 65816 actually has 15 8-bit registers, just not arranged in the most orthogonal way.

		

